{"prompt": "Generate a website for a sustainable fashion brand. The website should be user-friendly and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>EcoThreads - Sustainable Fashion</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #3b5998; /* A shade of blue */\n            --secondary-color: #a3b4d3; /* A lighter, complementary blue */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --light-text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #f4f6f8;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 50px 20px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .about-section, .products-section, .contact-section {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .about-section h2, .products-section h2, .contact-section h2 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 25px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .about-content, .product-grid, .contact-form {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .about-image {\n            flex: 1;\n            min-width: 300px;\n        }\n\n        .about-text {\n            flex: 1;\n            min-width: 300px;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .about-image img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .product-card {\n            background-color: var(--light-text-color);\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            width: 250px;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .product-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);\n        }\n\n        .product-card img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .product-card h3 {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .product-card p {\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .product-card .price {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input[type=\"text\"],\n        .contact-form input[type=\"email\"],\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            min-height: 120px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #2c4770; /* Darker shade of brand color */\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>EcoThreads</h1>\n        <p>Fashion that cares for the planet.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n        <a href=\"#products\">Products</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Consciously Crafted, Beautifully Worn</h2>\n            <p>Discover our collection of stylish and sustainable clothing made from eco-friendly materials. Join the movement towards a greener future.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"about-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Story</h2>\n            <div class=\"about-content\">\n                <div class=\"about-image\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/3b5998/ffffff?text=Sustainable+Fabric\" alt=\"Sustainable Fabric\">\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"about-text\">\n                    <p>At EcoThreads, we believe that fashion can be both beautiful and responsible. We are committed to using sustainable materials, ethical manufacturing processes, and reducing our environmental footprint. Our collections are designed to be timeless, versatile, and kind to the Earth.</p>\n                    <p>We source organic cotton, recycled polyester, and other innovative eco-fabrics to create pieces you'll love and feel good about wearing.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"products\" class=\"products-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Collections</h2>\n            <div class=\"product-grid\">\n                <div class=\"product-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x200/a3b4d3/333333?text=Organic+Tee\" alt=\"Organic Cotton T-Shirt\">\n                    <h3>Organic Cotton Tee</h3>\n                    <p>Soft, breathable, and made with 100% organic cotton.</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$35.00</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x200/a3b4d3/333333?text=Recycled+Jacket\" alt=\"Recycled Polyester Jacket\">\n                    <h3>Recycled Jacket</h3>\n                    <p>Lightweight and water-resistant, made from recycled bottles.</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$95.00</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/250x200/a3b4d3/333333?text=Linen+Pants\" alt=\"Linen Blend Pants\">\n                    <h3>Linen Blend Pants</h3>\n                    <p>Comfortable and chic, perfect for everyday wear.</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$70.00</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get in Touch</h2>\n            <div class=\"contact-form\">\n                <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                    <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                    <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                    <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                    <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n                </form>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 EcoThreads. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple scroll-to-section functionality\n        document.querySelectorAll('nav a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}